---
import BaseHead from '../../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <BaseHead title={"2. Jungian Archetypes | " + SITE_TITLE} description="2. Jungian Archetypes category page" />
    </head>
    <body>
        <Header />
        <main class="category-page" style="width: 75%; max-width: none; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
        <header style="margin-bottom: 40px;">
            <h1>2. Jungian Archetypes</h1>
        </header>

        <section class="category-article" style="margin-bottom: 40px; font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8;">
            <p>Carl Jung proposed the "Collective Unconscious," a reservoir of universal symbols shared by all humans. Dimensions of the psyche such as the Shadow (rejected self), the Anima/Animus (inner gender polarities), and the Wise Old Man appear in dreams to guide "individuation." Jung saw dreams as constructive messages for psychic integration. By recognizing these archetypes, individuals can transcend personal trauma and connect with the mythological layer of human experience.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="category-wp-content">
<figure class="wp-block-uagb-image__figure"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="/media-images/posts/jungian-archetypes-illustration-1.webp" alt="Illustration for 2. Jungian Archetypes" class="uag-image-1555" width="1200" height="550" title="2. Jungian Archetypes" role="img"></figure>
</section>



<section class="category-keywords" style="margin: 40px 0; padding: 20px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);">
    <h3 style="margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 1.3rem;">Related Keywords</h3>
    <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 10px;">
        <a href="/blog/jungian-dream-symbols-guide/" class="keyword-btn active" style="padding: 8px 16px; background-color: var(--accent, #A78BFA); color: #1A0E33; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.95rem; transition: opacity 0.2s;">#jungian dream analysis symbols list</a>
        <a href="/blog/jungian-shadow-dreams/" class="keyword-btn active" style="padding: 8px 16px; background-color: var(--accent, #A78BFA); color: #1A0E33; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.95rem; transition: opacity 0.2s;">#meaning of shadow in dreams jung</a>
        <a href="/blog/collective-unconscious-vs-personal-unconscious-examples/" class="keyword-btn active" style="padding: 8px 16px; background-color: var(--accent, #A78BFA); color: #1A0E33; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.95rem; transition: opacity 0.2s;">#collective unconscious vs personal unconscious examples</a>
        <a href="/blog/anima-and-animus-in-dreams/" class="keyword-btn active" style="padding: 8px 16px; background-color: var(--accent, #A78BFA); color: #1A0E33; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.95rem; transition: opacity 0.2s;">#anima and animus in dreams</a>
        <a href="/blog/individuation-process-through-dream-work/" class="keyword-btn active" style="padding: 8px 16px; background-color: var(--accent, #A78BFA); color: #1A0E33; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.95rem; transition: opacity 0.2s;">#individuation process through dream work</a>
    </div>
</section>




        


<div class="category-faq-section" style="margin-top: 60px; padding: 40px 30px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); backdrop-filter: blur(12px); -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px); border-radius: 16px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);">
    <h2 style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 40px; color: #E2DCF5; font-size: 2rem; font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.35);">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <div class="faq-content" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 24px;">

        <div class="faq-item" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); backdrop-filter: blur(12px); -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border-radius: 16px; padding: 24px; border-left: 4px solid var(--accent, #A78BFA); box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); transition: transform 0.2s ease;">
            <h4 style="color: var(--accent, #A78BFA); margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 600;">Q: What is the Shadow?</h4>
            <p style="color: #E2DCF5; margin: 0; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 1.05rem;"><strong>A:</strong> Hidden traits</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); backdrop-filter: blur(12px); -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border-radius: 16px; padding: 24px; border-left: 4px solid var(--accent, #A78BFA); box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); transition: transform 0.2s ease;">
            <h4 style="color: var(--accent, #A78BFA); margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 600;">Q: Are archetypes universal?</h4>
            <p style="color: #E2DCF5; margin: 0; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 1.05rem;"><strong>A:</strong> Yes, across cultures</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); backdrop-filter: blur(12px); -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border-radius: 16px; padding: 24px; border-left: 4px solid var(--accent, #A78BFA); box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); transition: transform 0.2s ease;">
            <h4 style="color: var(--accent, #A78BFA); margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 600;">Q: What is Individuation?</h4>
            <p style="color: #E2DCF5; margin: 0; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 1.05rem;"><strong>A:</strong> Psychological wholeness</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); backdrop-filter: blur(12px); -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border-radius: 16px; padding: 24px; border-left: 4px solid var(--accent, #A78BFA); box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); transition: transform 0.2s ease;">
            <h4 style="color: var(--accent, #A78BFA); margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 600;">Q: Can archetypes talk?</h4>
            <p style="color: #E2DCF5; margin: 0; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 1.05rem;"><strong>A:</strong> Yes, as personified figures</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); backdrop-filter: blur(12px); -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border-radius: 16px; padding: 24px; border-left: 4px solid var(--accent, #A78BFA); box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); transition: transform 0.2s ease;">
            <h4 style="color: var(--accent, #A78BFA); margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 600;">Q: Jung vs Freud?</h4>
            <p style="color: #E2DCF5; margin: 0; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 1.05rem;"><strong>A:</strong> Jung focus on growth, not just sex</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
    </main>
        <Footer />
    </body>
</html>
